commit.message:
Add -Wno-reserved-identifier to MaximumWarnings

Triggers on FD_ZERO() macro

Remove -Wno-return-std-move-in-c++11 from MaximumWarnings.cmake

Option no longer present in clang13.
Add flake-utils-like hepler functions for handling cross-compiling
Switch from defaultPackage to new packages.default
Change license header from GPL to zlib
Add tinycmmc.lib.versionFromFile helper function to Nix flake
Use two lines for version and name
Automatically add BUILD_TESTS and BUILD_EXTRA flags in TinyCMMC
Add more common defaults to TinyCMMC
Add TinyCMMC module that bundles common modules
Fix handling of targets with uppercase letters
Add support for 'git describe' style version numbers in VERSION file
Remove superfluous nix input from Nix flake
